metadata.name: Kanpai Panda EDC Pass
metadata.description: This Kanpai Panda EDC Pass 🐼🍻 provideds exclusive access to the largest electronic dance music festival 🕺🏻 in North America on May 21st, 2022!! EDC is an annual flagship event held at the Las Vegas Motor Speedway 🏎 that features art, 🎡 carnival rides (18 to be exact), circus-style performances 🤹🏻‍♂️, and the top EDM DJs in the world, including Diplo, Zedd, and Martin Garrix.
